            <Text fill="WHITE" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="In 1969 Ken Thompson and Dennis Ritchie of Bell Laboratories developed the UNIX operating system. It was later rewritten in C to make it more portable and eventually became a widely used operating system." wrappingWidth="722.0" VBox.vgrow="ALWAYS">
